# CAM::DOES_CAM_EXIST

## Summary
Does this camera still exist

## Parameters
* **CAMERA_INDEX** camera

## Returns
* **BOOL**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Returns whether or not the passed camera handle exists.
